      "text": "あむ……うん……熱々で、はふはふしちゃうけど……\n外はカリカリ、中はとろとろで、とっても美味しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yummy… Mmm… it's hot‚ and warm…\nIt's crispy on the outside‚ and tender on the inside‚ very delicious",
