      "text": "これは味噌ダレだよ。合うかな～って作ってみたの\n後は、思い切ってヨーグルトのソースも作ってみたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is miso sauce‚ I made it if it would go well~\nAnd‚ I made yogurt sauce with all my heart",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
